<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>31-5603.01</num>
  <heading>Registration requirement.</heading>
  <text>No person shall offer or sell a security in the District unless the security is registered under this chapter, the security or transaction is exempt under § <cite path="§31-5604.01">31-5604.01</cite> or § <cite path="§31-5604.02">31-5604.02</cite>, or the security is a federal covered security.</text>
